https://rubymonk.com/learning/books/1-ruby-primer/problems/156-sum

Your Sum

Problem Statement:
Given a custom class MyArray,
write a 'sum' method that takes a block parameter.

Example:
my_array = MyArray.new([1, 2, 3])
my_array.sum gives 6
my_array.sum(10) gives 16
my_array.sum(0) {|n| n ** 2 } gives 14

Tests:
gives the sum of all elements when no initial value or block is given
gives the sum of all elements and initial value when no block is given
evaluates the block and gives the sum of results when no inital value is given
evaluates the block and gives the sum of results and inital value